Connecting your product automatically updates your endpoint solution and provides you with the advanced management capabilities only available in Trend Vision One Endpoint Security. 
Note that your existing Trend Cloud One accounts also are updated and may require adjustment after the update.

children.chars:
The connection process only transfers information related to the product instance and base agents, but not existing XDR Endpoint Sensors. Contact your support representative to find out how to move Endpoint Sensor agents and any limitations that might impact your network. 

Trend Micro recommends transferring all product and base agent information before contacting support to ensure that XDR Endpoint Sensor agents can be properly associated with endpoints.  Learn more
